=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_UGen_ex20 ===

DESCRIPTION: A neutral pure_tone sound, with complex oscillator character around 402 Hz, featuring punchy attack and compressed envelope, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally simple.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: neutral
  crest_factor_db: compressed
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: simple
  spectral_flux_normalized: stable
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 402.3172
  harmonic_decay_rate: 1.8843
  harmonic_regularity: 0.0249
  pitch_clarity: 0.0706
  inharmonicity: 0.0000
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -5.9000
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
